@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@alex = course-alex-local-token
@riley = course-riley-local-token

### Reset, seed, and index the deterministic corpus
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/reset

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/seed

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/index

### Run Tenant Blue's golden evidence suite
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quality/rag/golden
Authorization: Bearer {{alex}}

### Run Tenant Red's suite; it must not return Tenant Blue or restricted evidence
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quality/rag/golden
Authorization: Bearer {{riley}}

### Prove insufficient context is a visible failed quality case
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/quality/rag/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{alex}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caseId": "missing-retention-policy",
  "question": "How long are audit logs retained?",
  "expectedEvidenceIds": ["article-audit-retention"]
}

### Inspect prompt structure and overlay/base resolution without exposing prompt bodies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quality/prompts
Authorization: Bearer {{alex}}

### Clear only derived vectors
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/vectors/clear

### Prove an empty index is an expected no-source result
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/quality/rag/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{alex}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caseId": "empty-index",
  "question": "How do I recover access?",
  "expectNoEvidence": true
}

### Restore evidence after the no-source case
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/index

### The local profile has no generation provider; this must be HTTP 503, never a canned answer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assistant/query
Authorization: Bearer {{alex}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What should I do after failed sign-ins locked my account?"
}
